MemoServ:
  This service provides the ability to send short notes to other users,
  even if they are offline. It can only be used by registered nicks, and
  memos can only be sent to registered nicks.
 
  This service is available to all users.
 
  Commands:
    SEND <nick> <memo text>
    READ [nick, for admins] <memoid>
    DEL [nick, for admins] <memoid/ALL>
    LIST [nick, for admins]
 
   Notice: For more Information type /msg MemoServ HELP <command>